snippet.textDisplay: There are a variety of instructions out there on making these masks...and not all match.  The type of material, the thickness, a 'filter' of some sort between the layers of cloth, T-shirts=yes...and T-shirts=no....should tie behind the ears AND over the head....anything is better than nothing...but making them to be the most protective possible...gets my vote.
